Episode list
Oreca card battles are one of the worlds most exciting contests. The kids love the game. One day, however, the characters on the cards mysteriously disappear, but one boy, Fire Orega, sees the cards appear in the real world and notices they are beginning to cause problems. Only by approaching a mysterious Oreca named Pandora can Fire hope to restore the cards to their normal forms, but it means he'll have to participate in real life Oreca Battles to do so.
